Privacy Policy
1. Introduction
Welcome to MiniMap Radar! This policy outlines the terms and conditions for downloading and using our app from the App Store. By downloading and using MiniMap Radar, you agree to this policy and our terms of service.
2. User Eligibility
To download and use MiniMap Radar, you must have a valid App Store account and be at least 13 years of age or the age of majority in your jurisdiction.
3. Privacy & Permissions
Geolocation:
MiniMap Radar uses your device's geolocation to provide and enhance the app's features. This data is not stored or shared with third parties. The app's functionalities depend on this data, and users are required to grant permission for the best experience.
Camera:
The app utilizes the device's camera to enable augmented reality features and identify markers. No imagery or data captured by the camera is stored or shared.
4. Usage Guidelines
Users must not use MiniMap Radar for any illegal or unauthorized purposes.
Respect other users. Harassment, abuse, or any form of hate speech will result in immediate actions to address the violation.
Any misuse of the app, including trying to exploit its features for personal gains, will be addressed according to App Store policies.
5. Intellectual Property
All content, design, graphics, and other components of MiniMap Radar are the property of MiniMap Radar and its creators. Unauthorized replication or use without explicit permission is prohibited.
6. Updates
Occasionally, we may release updates to MiniMap Radar. These can include bug fixes, new features, or general improvements. For the best user experience, we recommend always updating to the latest version.
7. Liability
While we aim to provide a flawless experience with MiniMap Radar, we cannot be held responsible for any issues, damages, or losses that result from app usage.
8. Support
For inquiries, issues, or support needs related to MiniMap Radar, please reach out to our support team at
timskap@gmail.com
.
9. Changes to This Policy
We may occasionally update this App Store Policy. Any modifications will be made known here, and users will be notified in the app or through the App Store listing.
10. Acceptance
By downloading and using MiniMap Radar, you express your agreement with this App Store Policy and commit to its terms.